==Host and Jury Board== This program was anchored initially by [[Rumana Malik Munmun]]. [[Chanchal Chowdhury]] and [[Mosharraf Karim]] later host the event. The members of Jury Board for television critics were Mamunur Rashid, [[Tariq Anam Khan]], [[Wahida Mollick Jolly]], Zahidur Rahman Anjan and Gaosul Alam Shaon.<ref>{{cite news |title=Meril- Prothom Alo award on Maasranga Television |url=http://archive.thedailystar.net/newDesign/news-details.php?nid=233320 |newspaper=The Daily Star |accessdate=10 September 2015}}</ref>
