==Course of Marathon== [[File:Buddhist monks in front of the Angkor Wat.jpg|thumb|300px|[[Angkor Wat]] is the site where marathon starts and ends.]] The Marathon starts and ends at the [[Angkor Wat]] temple complex, a [[World Heritage Site]]. Other important spots over course of run are the Angkor Archaeological Park, Preah Prom Rath pagoda, and several other temples.<ref name="khmertimeskh1"/>
