{{Infobox VG|title=Arya Vaiv |image= |developer=[[Megadream Software]] |publisher=[[Dongleware Verlags GmbH]] |designer= |engine= |released=1994 |genre=[[Shoot 'em up#Scrolling shooters|Scrolling shooter]] |modes=[[Single player]] |platforms=[[Amiga]], [[MS-DOS]] }}
'''''Arya Vaiv''''' is a 1994 [[computer game]] for the [[Amiga]] and [[MS-DOS]] platforms. It is a top-down [[space simulation|space]] [[Shoot 'em up#Scrolling shooters|shooter]] with available power-ups and a constant stream of enemies.
