{{Orphan|date=July 2015}} {{Infobox company | name = Bad Dragon Enterprises, Inc. | logo = Bad Dragon logo.png | logo_size = 200px | logo_alt = | logo_caption = Bad Dragon's logo | image = | image_size = | image_caption = | former_name = | type = | industry = [[Sex toys]] | founded = {{Start date and age|2008|06|}} | founders = {{Unbulleted list | Jan "Varka" Mulders | "Athus" | "Narse" | "Raith" }} | hq_location = | hq_location_city = [[Phoenix, Arizona|Phoenix]], [[Arizona]] | hq_location_country = [[United States|U.S.]] | area_served = Worldwide | key_people = | products = | num_employees = | num_employees_year = | parent = | subsid = | website = {{URL|bad-dragon.com}} | intl = }}
'''Bad Dragon Enterprises, Inc.''' is an [[United States|American]] manufacturer of fantasy-themed [[sex toy]]s. Products are sold online and at conventions.
==History== Bad Dragon was founded in June 2008.<ref name=sfbg>{{cite news |url=http://www.sfbg.com/pixel_vision/2012/09/20/werewolf-beats-all-interview-ceo-fantasy-sex-toy-site-bad-dragon |title=Werewolf beats all: Interview with the CEO of fantasy sex toy site Bad Dragon (NSFW) |first=Caitlin |last=Donohue |newspaper=[[San Francisco Bay Guardian]] |date=September 20, 2012 }}</ref><ref name=Dot>{{cite news |url=http://www.dailydot.com/business/bad-dragon-dildos-fantasy-sex/ |first=Brendan |last=O'Connor |title=Bad Dragon's green dildos are firing up the fantasy-sex market |newspaper=[[The Daily Dot]] |date=July 1, 2014 }}</ref> Jan "Varka" Mulders, one of the four co-founders (the others being "Athus", "Narse", and "Raith"), started making [[sex toy]]s in his college [[dormitory]] in [[Scotland]] the previous year.<ref name=sfbg/><ref name=Vice>{{cite news |url=https://www.vice.com/read/enter-the-dragon-v18n6 |first=Karley |last=Sciortino |title=Enter the Dragon |newspaper=[[Vice (magazine)|Vice]] |date=June 1, 2011 }}</ref> The company is now based in [[Arizona|Phoenix, Arizona]].<ref name=Vine>{{cite news |url=http://www.thevine.com.au/life/sex/giant-dragon-dildos-are-real-and-theyre-spectacular-20140702-283011/ |first=Jake |last=Cleland |title=Giant dragon dildos are real and they're spectacular |newspaper=The Vine |publisher=[[Fairfax Media]] |date=July 2, 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150405212257/http://thevine.com.au/life/sex/giant-dragon-dildos-are-real-and-theyre-spectacular-20140702-283011/ |archivedate=2015-04-05 |df= }}</ref>
==Products== {{As of|2017|11}}, Bad Dragon offers 61 [[dildo]]s, 20 [[Artificial vagina|penetrable toy]]s, 4 "wearables" (essentially a [[penis extension]]), 5 [[Packing (phallus)|packers]], 5 Lil' Vibes (smaller dildos that accompany a small bullet [[Vibrator (sex toy)|vibrator]]), 5 Lil' Squirts (very small dildos meant for testing the "Cumtube" feature), and various accessories and merchandise. All of their dildos are made of platinum-cured [[silicone]].<ref name=Dot/> The company's products are aimed at fantasy fans, including [[dragon]]s,<ref name=NY>{{cite news |url=http://nymag.com/thecut/2014/07/make-your-game-of-thrones-sex-fantasy-come-true.html |first=Allison P. |last=Davis |title=The Cut: Make Your ''Game of Thrones'' Sex Fantasy Come True |newspaper=[[New York magazine]] |date=July 2, 2014 }}</ref> [[horse]]s, [[orca]]s, [[Chimera (mythology)|chimera]]s, and [[werewolf|werewolves]].<ref name=Dot/><ref name=Vice/><ref>{{cite news |url=http://metro.co.uk/2014/07/02/these-dildos-are-shaped-to-look-like-dragon-penises-and-were-pretty-terrified-4783723/ |title=These dildos are shaped to look like dragon penises, and we’re pretty terrified |first=Hannah |last=Gale |newspaper=[[Metro (British newspaper)|Metro]] |date=July 2, 2014 }}</ref><ref name=Jezebel>{{cite web |url=http://jezebel.com/heres-the-giant-dragon-dildo-youve-been-writing-erotic-1598717678 |title=Here's the Giant Dragon Dildo You've Been Writing Erotic Fan-Fic About |first=Mark |last=Shrayber |website=[[Jezebel (website)|Jezebel]] |date=July 1, 2014 }}</ref> The website formerly gave a biography and picture for each character.<ref name=Vine/><ref name=NY/><ref name=Jezebel/> {{As of|2017|August|15|df=US}}, the website now has only picture of the sex toy in question and details about its physical attributes, although registered users can activate "Fantasy Mode", which replaces standard product descriptions and photos with stories, descriptions, and images that include references to fantasy or anthropomorphic themes. Bad Dragon also offers a [[Three-dimensional space|3-D]] interactive model to view certain areas of each toy. Products are cast by hand and can be extensively customized, with a choice of colors including special requests of firmness, and of [[dildo]] length;<ref name=Vice/> customers can also submit their own designs, some of which are chosen for special production.<ref name=Dot/> Dildos can be ordered with a [[suction cup]] that is actually a concave area on the bottom of the dildo, and a "Cumtube" to simulate [[ejaculation]];<ref name=Vine/> the company sells "Cum Lube".<ref name=Dot/><ref name=Jezebel/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cracked.com/article_17372_18-more-worlds-most-disturbing-sex-toys.html |first=Ian |last=Fortey |title=18 More of the World's Most Disturbing Sex Toys #12. The Drippy Dragon |website=[[Cracked.com]] |date=May 18, 2009 }}</ref>
==In popular culture== Bad Dragon is featured in the [[nerd culture]] documentary ''[[Traceroute (film)|Traceroute]]''.<ref>{{cite web |first=Peter |last=Mühlbauer |url=http://www.heise.de/tp/artikel/47/47614/1.html |title=Über den Raum in die Zeit |website=Telepolis |publisher=[[Heinz Heise|Heise Online]] |language=German |date=March 7, 2015 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Chris |last=Higgins |url=http://mentalfloss.com/article/79393/traceroute-documentary-about-nerds-and-annihilation |title='Traceroute,' A Documentary about Nerds and Annihilation |website=[[Mental Floss]] |date=May 1, 2016 }}</ref>
