{{Infobox person
| name         = Khánh Thy
| image        = 
| caption      = Khánh Thy at Vietnam Open Dancesport Championship 2009
| birth_name   = Khánh Thy
| occupation   = Dancer
| years_active = 2002–present
| partner      = Phan Hiển
}}

'''Khánh Thy''' is the grand master of [[Dancesport]] of [[Vietnam]]. Khánh Thy and professional dancer Chí Anh used to dance as a couple, but after achieving success, Khánh Thy went on to dance with Phan Hiển who remains her partner to date. She has won many awards in Dancesport, including two Vietnam Open Dancesport Championship Awards, an AIG Award and a [[SEA Games]]. With so much success, she has become the grandmaster of Dancesport in Vietnam.<ref>[https://translate.google.com/translate?hl=en&sl=&tl=en&u=http%3A%2F%2Fbaodatviet.vn%2FHome%2Fvanhoa%2FNguyen-Hung-nhay-cung-Khanh-Thy%2F20118%2F164097.datviet Báo Đất Việt]. 27 August 2011</ref><ref>[https://translate.google.com/translate?hl=en&sl=&tl=en&u=http%3A%2F%2Fhanoimoi.com.vn%2Fnewsdetail%2FVan-hoa%2F518986%2Fkhanh-thythu-minh-thoi-lua-am-nhac-thang-8.htm Hà Nội Mới]. 2 August 2011</ref>

